                <button class="copy-command" type="button" data-copy="bun install&#10;bun run validate">copy</button>
              </div>
              <pre><code>bun install
bun run validate</code></pre>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="path-card reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 180ms">
            <p class="claim">3 / IMPLEMENT</p>
            <h3>Build</h3>
            <p>Use the TypeScript and Rust reference packages as executable anchors for conformant behavior.</p>
            <a href="../packages/core/README.md">TypeScript</a>
            <a href="../packages/core-rs/README.md">Rust</a>
          </article>
        </div>
